Arcade DISSIDA FINAL FANTASY


Arcade "DISSIDIA FINAL FANTASY" is a 3vs3 online party action game where you can control characters
from past Final Fantasy series and enjoy exhilarating action battles! Characters, stages, and BGM appear from past FF series! This is a new ``Final Fantasy'' that elevates RPG battles to complete party action battles, such as ``EX skills'' that support party members and `` summons'' that can be summoned to fight together .
